  "description": "A registered replication report dataset examining the psychometric properties of error-related negativity (ERN) and error positivity (Pe) components derived from EEG recordings. Raw EGI MFF files were processed using EEGLAB, with task-specific events recoded into response-locked and stimulus-locked ERN/Pe-relevant event labels, and converted to BIDS format for standardized data sharing and reproducibility.",
  "methods_description": "Raw EEG data were acquired using EGI systems and recorded in MFF format. Data were imported and processed using EEGLAB, with task-specific events recoded into response-locked and stimulus-locked event labels relevant to ERN/Pe analysis. Processed data were exported to BIDS format.",
